private java.lang.String messageId
Identifier of the message. In the case of a new client request, this is a newly-generated message ID. In the case of a server response to a request, this is the original message ID from the request.

destinationAddress

private java.lang.String destinationAddress
Address of the message destination application. In the case of a server response to a request, this is address of the sender who originally made the request.

destinationName

private java.lang.String destinationName
Name of the message destination application. In the case of a server response to a request, this is name of the sender who originally made the request.
